<li id="cite_note-FOOTNOTEFaszcza202114–15-10"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-FOOTNOTEFaszcza202114–15_10-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="#CITEREFFaszcza2021">Faszcza 2021</a>, pp.&#160;14–15.</span>
