<li id="cite_note-FOOTNOTETaylor201981-63"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-FOOTNOTETaylor201981_63-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="#CITEREFTaylor2019">Taylor 2019</a>, p.&#160;81.</span>
