<li id="cite_note-FOOTNOTETaylor201976,_82-64"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-FOOTNOTETaylor201976,_82_64-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="#CITEREFTaylor2019">Taylor 2019</a>, pp.&#160;76, 82.</span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-65"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-65">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="#CITEREFTaylor2019">Taylor 2019</a>, p.&#160;89, citing <a href="#CITEREFSall._Iug.">Sall. <i>Iug.</i></a>, 51.3, where amid an uncertain battle "Metellus... opposed four legionary cohorts to the enemy's infantry", pushed through, and won the <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_the_Muthul" title="Battle of the Muthul">battle</a>.</span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-66"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-66">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="#CITEREFTaylor2019">Taylor 2019</a>, p.&#160;82, citing <cite id="CITEREFBell1965" class="citation journal cs1">Bell, Michael J V (1965). "Tactical reform in the Roman republican army". <i>Historia: Zeitschrift für Alte Geschichte</i>. <b>14</b> (4): 404–422. <a href="/wiki/ISSN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISSN (identifier)">ISSN</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.worldcat.org/issn/0018-2311">0018-2311</a>. <a href="/wiki/JSTOR_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="JSTOR (identifier)">JSTOR</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.jstor.org/stable/4434897">4434897</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Historia%3A+Zeitschrift+f%C3%BCr+Alte+Geschichte&amp;rft.atitle=Tactical+reform+in+the+Roman+republican+army&amp;rft.volume=14&amp;rft.issue=4&amp;rft.pages=404-422&amp;rft.date=1965&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jstor.org%2Fstable%2F4434897%23id-name%3DJSTOR&amp;rft.issn=0018-2311&amp;rft.aulast=Bell&amp;rft.aufirst=Michael+J+V&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AMarian+reforms" class="Z3988"></span></span>
</li>
