<li id="cite_note-70"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-70">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite id="CITEREFTweedie2011" class="citation journal cs1">Tweedie, Fiona C (2011). "The case of the missing veterans: Roman colonisation and veteran settlement in the second century BC". <i>Historia: Zeitschrift für Alte Geschichte</i>. <b>60</b> (4): 458–473. <a href="/wiki/Doi_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="Doi (identifier)">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://doi.org/10.25162%2Fhistoria-2011-0019">10.25162/historia-2011-0019</a>. <a href="/wiki/ISSN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISSN (identifier)">ISSN</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.worldcat.org/issn/0018-2311">0018-2311</a>. <a href="/wiki/JSTOR_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="JSTOR (identifier)">JSTOR</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.jstor.org/stable/41342861">41342861</a>. <a href="/wiki/S2CID_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="S2CID (identifier)">S2CID</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://api.semanticscholar.org/CorpusID:252451787">252451787</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Historia%3A+Zeitschrift+f%C3%BCr+Alte+Geschichte&amp;rft.atitle=The+case+of+the+missing+veterans%3A+Roman+colonisation+and+veteran+settlement+in+the+second+century+BC&amp;rft.volume=60&amp;rft.issue=4&amp;rft.pages=458-473&amp;rft.date=2011&amp;rft.issn=0018-2311&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fapi.semanticscholar.org%2FCorpusID%3A252451787%23id-name%3DS2CID&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jstor.org%2Fstable%2F41342861%23id-name%3DJSTOR&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.25162%2Fhistoria-2011-0019&amp;rft.aulast=Tweedie&amp;rft.aufirst=Fiona+C&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AMarian+reforms" class="Z3988"></span></span>
