<li id="cite_note-FOOTNOTEKeaveney200763–64-71"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-FOOTNOTEKeaveney200763–64_71-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="#CITEREFKeaveney2007">Keaveney 2007</a>, pp.&#160;63–64.</span>
